snippet.title: VOID DASH TEASER TRAILER
snippet.description:
VOID DASH TEASER TRAILER

A simple endless runner arcade game about dodging dangerous asteroids.
Use powerups to break your highscore and collect Voidbucks to unlock new skins in the shop. 

Download on itch: https://pyrophoricgames.itch.io/voiddash
Download on google play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PyrophoricGames.VOIDDASH&pcampaignid=web_share
Website: https://pyrophoric.games
